{
  "stem": "628.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She is able to work at 17-- a working girl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she has to do-- separation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Oye!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Oh, that.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My grandmas and I got mad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "No!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Don't take my Gisa!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Don't!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I, too-- [SOBBING] my sister, my beautiful girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I didn't know, then, where.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was a fighting going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I thought, I don't let that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But my sister said to me, Hellmuchin, she said, you stay with Opa and Oma.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You don't have to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Look after them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It's your duty now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Next day, she was gone-- deported-- to the train, somewhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I was with my grandparents, and alone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I became, suddenly, very strong-- strong boy, of 13.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Having-- suddenly, I became 20.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I said, that's your duty now, to look after these two.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We went, four or five days after, to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We arrived in March-- got in on deportation-- end of the March, or something, in Theresienstadt, 40s-- '43.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Arriving in Theresienstadt, in the ghetto, we went on ordinary train then, with seats, and every-- everybody was on it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We had luggage-- what you took with you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, normal travelling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The furniture you have to leave behind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the all-- the servant, all that, you couldn't take with you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH], everything had to stay there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like mention-- mentioned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a hard train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, for me, it was a train, as a child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I saw, already what-- where are we going?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What-- what's happening here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the [NON-ENGLISH]!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Definitely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you think-- and it was-- how do you call it-- springtime.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it's a good thing that was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when we got into Theresienstadt, I was with my grandmother, together.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
